&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;Where are you now? Atlantis. Under the sea. Under the sea. Where are you now? Another dream. The monster&#39;s running wild inside of me. I&#39;m faded. I&#39;m faded. So lost, I&#39;m faded. I&#39;m faded. So lost, I&#39;m faded.    Where are you now? Atlantis. Under the sea. Under the sea. Where are you now? Another dream. The monster&#39;s running wild inside of me. I&#39;m faded. I&#39;m faded. So lost, I&#39;m faded. I&#39;m faded. So lost, I&#39;m faded.

